{"id": "5138", "post": "<div class=\"post-5138 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-virtual-servers tag-canada tag-exclusive tag-montreal tag-servarica tag-xen\" id=\"post-5138\"><h2 class=\"storytitle\"><a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/blog/servarica-7month-1gb-or-48year-768mb-xen-vps-in-montreal-canada/\" rel=\"bookmark\">Servarica \u2013 $7/month 1GB or $48/year 768MB Xen VPS in Montreal, Canada</a></h2><div class=\"meta\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" data-src=\"/media/icons/tag_green.png\" alt=\"Tags: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/canada/\" rel=\"tag\">canada</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/exclusive/\" rel=\"tag\">exclusive</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/montreal/\" rel=\"tag\">Montreal</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servarica/\" rel=\"tag\">servarica</a>, <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/xen/\" rel=\"tag\">xen</a> <img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/media/icons/calendar.png\" alt=\"Date/Time: \" class=\"litespeed-loaded\" data-was-processed=\"true\"> May 2, 2014 @ 1:00 pm, by Maarten Kossen</div><div class=\"storycontent tablelook\"><p><a href=\"http://servarica.com\"><img data-lazyloaded=\"1\" src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/serveracia.jpg.webp\" class=\"screenshot litespeed-loaded\" data-src=\"https://lowendbox.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/serveracia.jpg.webp\" alt=\"Servarica\" data-was-processed=\"true\"></a>Hani, from <a href=\"http://servarica.com\">Servarica</a>, is back with two exclusive offers located in Canada. Those who are not big fans of PRISM or the Patriot act will probably like the location and it\u2019s low ping to the USA. Servarica have been a registered company in province of Quebec for more than 3 years. We have featured them <a href=\"https://lowendbox.com/tag/servarica-com/\">two times before</a>, the last time was in August 2013. As well as being a VPS provider, they\u2019re also a software development form who develop control panel / management software for Citrix XenServers. This gives them a very good knowledge of how Xen works, which hugely benefits them as a provider. Their nodes are using brand new Supermicro servers with 2 X E5-2560, ECC DDR3 memory and \u201chigh end redundant networking devices\u201d. These server are the basis of their high availability structure, together with a SAN. Servers are set up instantly unless you are flagged for manual review, in which case it could take up to 8 hours. Please leave your reviews below.</p><table><tbody><tr><td><strong>LEB Special 1</strong><p></p><ul><li>1GB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU</li><li>20GB SAN SSD-cached disk space</li><li>1TB bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>1x /64 IPv6 on request</li><li>Free daily backups</li><li>Free HA/failover</li><li>Xen-PV/Custom</li><li>$7/month</li><li><a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=198\" target=\"_blank\">Order here</a></li></ul></td><td><strong>LEB Special 2</strong><p></p><ul><li>768GB RAM</li><li>1 vCPU</li><li>15GB SAN SSD-cached disk space</li><li>1TB bandwidth</li><li>1Gbps uplink</li><li>1x IPv4 address</li><li>1x /64 IPv6 on request</li><li>Free daily backups</li><li>Free HA/failover</li><li>Xen-PV/Custom</li><li>$48/year</li><li><a href=\"https://servarica.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=176\">Order here</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-5138\"></span><br>\nServarica accept payments via Paypal (credit cards are accepted through paypal). Offer from a proxy or a non-domestic IP address are not accepted and could delay your order. For this offer, they\u2019re providing a 7 days full refund policy with no question asked. Canadians will have to pay GST and PST tax. Additional IPv4s are billed at $2 per month or $12/year. Their TOS/AUP can be <a href=\"http://servarica.com/terms-of-service/\">viewed here</a>.</p><p>This is the SLA they provide regarding uptime:</p><p>99.9% and above \u2013&gt; normal operation<br>\n99.0% and above \u2013&gt; 15% refund of monthly charges<br>\n97.0% and above \u2013&gt; 30% refund of monthly charges<br>\n95.0% and above \u2013&gt; 50% refund of monthly charges<br>\nLess than 95% \u2013&gt; 100% refund of monthly charges</p><p><strong>Network Information</strong></p><p>Servers are located at the Cologix Datacenter in Montreal. They operate their our own multi-homed network and have their own AS number. Their network is fully redundant with redundant routers and switches.</p><p>Test IPv4: 204.93.54.203<br>\nTest File: <a href=\"http://204.93.54.203/file_100MB.bin\">http://204.93.54.203/file_100MB.bin</a></p><p class=\"dpsp-share-text\"></p><div id=\"dpsp-content-bottom\" class=\"dpsp-content-wrapper dpsp-shape-rounded dpsp-column-auto dpsp-has-spacing dpsp-no-labels dpsp-show-on-mobile dpsp-button-style-1 dpsp-has-icon-background dpsp-has-button-background dpsp-show-total-share-count dpsp-show-total-share-count-after\"><ul class=\"dpsp-networks-btns-wrapper dpsp-networks-btns-content dpsp-has-button-icon-animation\"><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservarica-7month-1gb-or-48year-768mb-xen-vps-in-montreal-canada%2F&amp;t=Servarica%20-%20%247%2Fmonth%201GB%20or%20%2448%2Fyear%20768MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Montreal%2C%20Canada\" class=\"dpsp-network-btn dpsp-facebook dpsp-no-label dpsp-first\" title=\"Share on Facebook\"><span class=\"dpsp-network-icon\"></span><span class=\"dpsp-network-label-wrapper\"></span></a></li><li><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Servarica%20-%20%247%2Fmonth%201GB%20or%20%2448%2Fyear%20768MB%20Xen%20VPS%20in%20Montreal%2C%20Canada&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flowendbox.com%2Fblog%2Fservarica-7month-1gb-or-48year-768mb-xen-vps-in-montreal-canada%2F&amp;via=LowEndNetwork\" class=\"d